{
  "stem": "13457.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that was the first time in good many month that we went to, to, to a place where I really had a lot of bread.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't know whether I had enough of bread, but I wasn't hungry anymore.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I also was getting some kind of a food quote, unquote 'supplement' from a friend-- a colleague of mine that was an orphan sitting next to me in the classroom.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he was giving me [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] are the pressings from, from sunflower seeds.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The oil usually goes to humans, and the, the leftover from these pressings is usually given to the animals, to the horses for, for their consumption.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this kid was stealing the [NON-ENGLISH] from some horse.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He found some stable.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so he was steeling enough for himself.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was bringing it to school.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's what kept me going for quite awhile because otherwise, there was really days there was nothing to eat.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So then once my father was out of jail, he got his hair cut.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had the first loaf of bread.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We gave a little bit of vodka, little bottle, to the train station commandant, and he put us on train because my father said that if I don't go-- don't get the hell out of here in a hurry, they may change their mind.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They will lock me up again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And sometimes they were locking and sometimes they were also, apparently, shooting even though I don't know whether it can be substantiated historically because apparently, they did not shoot at the time.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were just sending to fr-- to the front.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But anyway, we got out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We got on the train, and we came to, to south of Russia.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "To be precise, it was near Tashkent.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
